      "description": "Usable fair-condition driver being sold as-is. This car shows its age with noticeable cosmetic wear, blemishes, and general imperfections inside and out, and it has a tired overall presentation rather than a polished one. That said, it remains a serviceable car for someone looking for an affordable driver in this model without paying good-condition money. Best suited for a buyer who wants an honest, older car and understands it is not a showpiece.",
