      "description": "$46,900 - Exceptional vehicle in mint condition and ready for its next owner. It presents beautifully inside and out, with a very clean body, well-kept interior, and the kind of overall appearance and feel you expect from a top-tier example. It runs and drives exactly as it should, with no notable needs apparent, and has clearly been kept to a very high standard. If you want a used vehicle that stands out for condition rather than one that needs sorting, this is the kind of car worth seeing.",
