      "description": "A classic with plenty of character and a nice driver-quality feel. It runs and drives, presents decently overall, and looks like something you can enjoy as-is while improving over time. This isn\u2019t a show car, and it does have visible age, wear, and cosmetic imperfections, but it\u2019s an honest, usable vintage car with charm and potential.",
